item.title: CVE-2020-5030|2024-09-17T02:15:54.821Z -- ibm -- rational%20rhapsody%20model%20manager
item.description: IBM Jazz Foundation and IBM Engineering products are vulnerable to cross-site scripting. This vulnerability allows users to embed arbitrary JavaScript code in the Web UI thus altering the intended functionality potentially leading to credentials disclosure within a trusted session. IBM X-Force ID: 193737.
